Add a Wayfinder (trial) user.

Parameters:
passwd Set to the password of the user.
userKey The licence to add user for, NULL if none.
userItem Set to the the new user.
startTime The start time of initial access.
endTime The end time of initial access. If same as startTime then no start acces right is added.
regionID The region of initial access.
lang The language of the client.
clientType The clientType, NULL if none.
clientTypeOptions The clientTypeOptions, NULL if none.
programV Vector of three uint32.
activationCode The activation code used to create user, empty if not so.
extraTypes Some extra types of UserRights to add.
createWFST The WFST to use, default TRIAL.
transactionDays The number of transaction days, default 0.
brand The brand of the user, defualt empty.
fixedUserName The fixed user name to use, default NULL.
extraComment Extra text added to operatorcomment.
extraElements Elements to add to user, elements are owned by userItem after call.
userNamePrefix The explicitly set user name prefix, uses default if NULL. Overrides fixedUserName if not NULL.
email The email address to set in user, NULL if none.
name The name to set in user, split into first and last name, NULL if none.
opt_in_name The name of customer contact info to set.
opt_in_value The value to set for opt_in_name.
extraRights additional rights for user
Returns:
0 all is ok, 2 if timeout, 3 if error and 4 if an UserIDKey of type account isn't unique.

Add a Wayfinder (trial) user for a licence key.

Checks for hardware key activation code, IMEI:00440000113342.

Parameters:
passwd Set to the password of the user.
server Set to the server name if redirect.
userKey The licence to add user for, NULL if none.
userItem Set to the the new user.
startTime The start time of initial access.
endTime The end time of initial access. If same as startTime then no start acces right is added.
regionID The region of initial access.
lang The language of the client.
clientType The clientType, NULL if none.
clientTypeOptions The clientTypeOptions, NULL if none.
programV Vector of three uint32.
activationCode The activation code used to create user, empty if not so.
extraTypes Some extra types of UserRights to add.
createWFST The WFST to use, default TRIAL.
transactionDays The number of transaction days, default 0.
brand The brand of the user, defualt empty.
fixedUserName The fixed user name to use, default NULL.
extraComment Extra text added to operatorcomment.
extraElements Elements to add to user, elements are owned by userItem after call.
userNamePrefix The explicitly set user name prefix, uses default if NULL. Overrides fixedUserName if not NULL.
email The email address to set in user, NULL if none.
name The name to set in user, split into first and last name, NULL if none.
opt_in_name The name of customer contact info to set.
opt_in_value The value to set for opt_in_name.
extraRights additional rights for user
autoKey The licence to check for auto activation, NULL if none.
Returns:
0 all is ok, 2 if timeout, 3 if error, 4 if redirect, 5 if may not create user.
